    "home_about_section_VcUBXT": {
      "type": "home-about-section",
      "name": "Home About",
      "settings": {
        "about_image": "shopify://shop_images/Group_306_774cd721-a6f3-4089-b5b1-216d9de4793a.png",
        "subheading": "About Us",
        "heading": "Welcome to Pawcredible",
        "content": "<h4>where with every bite, your dog gets a little closer to his or her healthiest, happiest self.</h4><p>At Pawcredible, we believe dogs deserve more than just food, they deserve real nourishment. That's why we created a unique freeze dried blend from nature and perfected by science. Our recipe contains no preservatives, no fillers, No Grains, and not a single man-made vitamin or mineral-because only the very best bioavailable ingredients belong in your dog's bowl.</p><p>We care about nourishing your dog's health from nose to tail. Each ingredient is carefully chosen for what it gives your dog, not just what’s left out..</p><p>The payoff? Products that promote more than 10 vital health benefits, including:</p><ul><li>A Calmer, Happier Personality: Less anxiety and stress, more tail wags</li><li>Shinier Coats & Joint Support: For dogs that enjoy running and playing</li><li>Stronger Immune System: Superfoods defend against allergies and daily challenges</li><li>Easy Digestion: Bioavailable ingredients mean more regular, comfortable poops</li><li>Sharper Brain & Focus: Healthy fats like EPA & DHA fuel learning and attentiveness</li><li>Improved Gut Health: Prebiotics help your dog's beneficial gut bacteria grow strong</li><li>Healthy Energy Levels: Antioxidant polyphenols maintain your dog's energy throughout the day</li><li>Longer, Happier Life: Our blend of raw ingredients, veggies, and fruits delivers maximum nutrition in every meal</li><li>Oral Health: Healthier teeth and gums, for fresh doggy smiles</li><li>Happy Hormones: Serotonin support helps your dog be more in the moment and engaged with you</li><li>Food should nourish, not pass through. That’s why we make every bowl count.</li></ul><p>Join us in our mission to help dogs thrive naturally, happily, and incredibly.</p><p>Because your dog isn’t just a pet, they’re family. And every family member deserves the best.</p>"
      }
    },
    "home_content1_xWbU7p": {
      "type": "home-content1",
      "name": "Home Content1",
      "settings": {
        "content1_heading": "Pure Chicken. Superfood Powered. Freeze-Dried to Perfection.",
        "main_image": "shopify://shop_images/Group_299_1.png",
        "col1_heading": "Why It Matters?",
        "col1_text": "Made with 75% real chicken and freeze-dried to preserve raw nutrition, our treats pack clean protein with functional superfoods like pumpkin, cranberries, turmeric, and seaweed. Every piece supports vitality, digestion, and immune health, all in a form dogs love.",
        "col2_heading": "What Makes It Different?",
        "col2_text": "Unlike standard freeze-dried treats that are just meat, our Raw Fusion treats go further. We fuse the highest quality chicken with a spectrum of scientifically chosen superfoods and prebiotics, delivering a unique balance of taste and targeted wellness. It’s not just a snack; it’s nutrition with purpose.",
        "col3_heading": "How It Fits Into Your Dog’s Life?",
        "col3_text": "Whether you’re training, rewarding, or topping up meals, the Raw Fusion Treat Pouch is designed for everyday flexibility. Lightweight and mess-free, it’s perfect for walks, hikes, or travel. One pouch brings convenience, health, and joy into every moment you share with your dog."
      }
    },
