        "testimonial_rK7xYC": {
          "type": "testimonial",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Game Changer for Our Mealtime Routine",
            "review": "Never thought I’d write a review about dog food, but here we are. Our Goldendoodle, Maple, used to nibble at her kibble like it was a chore. Since switching to Pawcredible, she finishes her bowl in minutes. Her digestion is smoother, her coat looks shinier, and she genuinely seems happier at mealtimes. This kibble has been a total win for us.",
